    "description": "Grow your career with Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Assistant Store Manager for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nAsian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
